# RSA private keys for pinning per-env extension IDs. The matching
# base64 public key in .env.{mode} is public-by-design (it's literally
# the `key` field that ships in the published manifest) but the .pem
# must never be checked in.
keys/

# Per-mode env (root .gitignore also covers these — duplicated here
# for clarity since they pair with keys/ above).
.env.staging
.env.production
.env.local
